  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LAYERED ORDEAL is a bullet time FPS. Face and defeat various bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello Child.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have awakened from sleep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We will give you many ordeals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for the lowest level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/68617ec80e3072331c7a06abbdd0effe.avif?t=1742445945\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flexible Bullet time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time goes into slow motion when the player is stationary. The enemy's weak spot will always move around and hide its appearance. Aim at the moment the weak spot appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/5620316d1707838cd3a04668463864b1.poster.avif?t=1742445945\" width=534 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/5620316d1707838cd3a04668463864b1.webm?t=1742445945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/5620316d1707838cd3a04668463864b1.mp4?t=1742445945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Massive Bullet hell</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The enemy will shoot multiple bullets at you. Take advantage of the Bullet Time feature to avoid them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/c128e62a337f30442209cfe3c0e69f09.poster.avif?t=1742445945\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/c128e62a337f30442209cfe3c0e69f09.webm?t=1742445945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/c128e62a337f30442209cfe3c0e69f09.mp4?t=1742445945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through battles, credit can be earned and abilities can be increased.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/b7ccf458d240d2cdf5021be897888bf1.avif?t=1742445945\" width=600 height=156 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LAYERED ORDEAL is a bullet time FPS. Face and defeat various bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello Child.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have awakened from sleep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We will give you many ordeals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for the lowest level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/68617ec80e3072331c7a06abbdd0effe.avif?t=1742445945\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flexible Bullet time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time goes into slow motion when the player is stationary. The enemy's weak spot will always move around and hide its appearance. Aim at the moment the weak spot appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/5620316d1707838cd3a04668463864b1.poster.avif?t=1742445945\" width=534 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/5620316d1707838cd3a04668463864b1.webm?t=1742445945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/5620316d1707838cd3a04668463864b1.mp4?t=1742445945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Massive Bullet hell</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The enemy will shoot multiple bullets at you. Take advantage of the Bullet Time feature to avoid them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/c128e62a337f30442209cfe3c0e69f09.poster.avif?t=1742445945\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/c128e62a337f30442209cfe3c0e69f09.webm?t=1742445945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/c128e62a337f30442209cfe3c0e69f09.mp4?t=1742445945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through battles, credit can be earned and abilities can be increased.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151330/extras/b7ccf458d240d2cdf5021be897888bf1.avif?t=1742445945\" width=600 height=156 /></span></p>",
